  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluating the efficacy of Valsalva's maneuver and music therapy on peripheral venous
      cannulation pain and anxiety
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      One hundred and fifty patients undergoing surgery were randomized to apply Valsalva's
      maneuver (the valsalva group) and music therapy(the music group) and a placebo (the control
      group) during peripheral venous cannulation (PVC). The patients' pain, anxiety, and
      satisfaction scores will be measured.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
